{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For those who want classical tower defense experience Tower Petroleum gives towers, tower upgrades, monsters, economical upgrades and strategic experience <strong>like you had before!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tower Petroleum has a narrative element to it. Every choice you make, shaped by your own moral compass, forges a unique path, not only influencing the story but also defining your entire gameplay experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/TP-character012_1.png?t=1729451060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique levels with different strategic possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/levels.png?t=1729451060\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different branches of towers upgrades: feed your enemies lead or disintegrate them with deadly plasma, use drones or fire: whatever fits your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/upgrades.png?t=1729451060\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">18 unique monsters: deadly sharktopuses, hideous roll-eyed-grapplers, dark-matter crawlers. Look in the eyes of abyss and try to stay sane.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/monsters_animation.gif?t=1729451060\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A deep story with moral choices. Who will you become: a cold-blooded monster who does what it takes to try to save what left of human race or will you try to find compassion and kindness in those shivering deserts. Your choices will give you unique traits that will define y